& [Realization_002_RareBoundaryWitnessesStayPeripheral] is a dense-node refinement
  + [subjects] is Fermat-prime identity, Fermat-number factor periphery, Mersenne primes, and base-2 Wieferich primes
  + [observation] is Fermat-number factor periphery appears only in (0, 1000], base-2 Wieferich primes appear in (1000, 2000] and (2000, 5000], and a Fermat-prime identity increment appears in (50000, 100000]
