  + [meaning] is broad linked-prime families are better candidates for finite sampling comparisons, but still not controlling mechanisms
  + [boundary] is a better sampling surface is not RH evidence

& [Realization_004_PsiRequiresPrimePowerAttention] is a toolchain realization
  + [subject] is psi(x)-x interval movement
  + [observation] is psi sign flips while theta sign does not in this finite pass
  + [meaning] is any RH-landscape bridge that uses psi must also inspect prime powers, not only prime family membership
